item.title: CVE-2022-1098|2024-09-16T19:36:21.828Z -- diaenerrgie -- diaenergie
item.description: Delta Electronics DIAEnergie (all versions prior to 1.8.02.004) are vulnerable to a DLL hijacking condition. When combined with the Incorrect Default Permissions vulnerability of 4.2.2 above, this makes it possible for an attacker to escalate privileges
